title: Go Barefoot - Routes(2014)
description:
Go Barefoot - Routes

Go Barefoots first ep, a fusion of sounds from both Africa and the western world.


Tracklist:

1. You Don't Have to Go
2. I Won't Back Down
3. Climb Through the Window
4. Johannesburg
5. Stand Up Saul
6. Grazing

They released their ep for free, so no reason to feel guilty torrenting it. But if you love it and you want to offer them some support you can buy the Ep on band camp for a selected amount:
or just buy it on itunes etc
